---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Founding Member Offer"
  description="Early access to Clarity. Support Plans with added benefits and limited seats"
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/founding-offer"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Founding Member Offer</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      A limited opportunity to shape Clarity. from the inside.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    class="mb-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gray-900 text-white dark:bg-black/50 rounded-lg px-8 py-12 mb-24 text-center"
  >
    <div class="mb-6 grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-left text-sm md:text-base">
      <div>
        <p class="text-left">
          We're inviting a small group of early supporters to access Clarity.
          Support Plans before public launch.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-left">
          This is your opportunity to get more hands-on support, help shape the
          service, and lock in early pricing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-left">
          You'll receive additional input during onboarding, early access to new
          tools and frameworks, and a direct line to the people behind Clarity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What Founding Members Get</h2>
  <section
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left mb-6 px-4"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Priority onboarding and early session slots</li>
        <li>Extended async support in your first 90 days</li>
        <li>Access to new tools before public release</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Private feedback channel to help shape the offer</li>
        <li>Locked-in pricing for your first year</li>
        <li>Option to remain fully anonymous</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <blockquote
    class="mb-24 italic text-center mt-6 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300"
  >
    “This is your opportunity to shape and influence the support you will
    receive.”
  </blockquote>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What We Ask in Return</h2>
  <section
    class="max-w-xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-6 text-center justify-center items-center mb-24 px-4"
  >
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
    >
      <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Willingness to share short feedback at key moments</li>
        <li>
          Participation in shaping how Clarity. evolves<br />
        </li>
        <li>Optional testimonial to build future confidence</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">When It Starts</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        We're onboarding founding members in June 2025. <br />
        If you're already on the waitlist, you'll hear from us directly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="my-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Want to be considered?
      </p>
      <a
        href="/#waitlist"
        class="inline-block bg-black text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:opacity-90 transition"
      >
        Join the Waitlist
      </a>
    </section>
  </section>
</Base>
